headline: Tyler Technologies (TYL): Evaluating Valuation Following Major Fulton County Cloud Software Win
summary: Tyler Technologies (TYL) just landed a key client win that is bound to catch the attention of investors debating their next move. The company has announced a deal with the Fulton County Clerk’s office in Georgia to implement its Enterprise Records Management solution, powered by Amazon Web Services. For Tyler, this is more than a routine contract; it builds on an ongoing relationship with Fulton County and signals strong demand for its advanced, cloud-based public sector software. For anyone...
